Title: Jaguars face tough decision on OT Cam Robinson
Description: With more than $74 million in available cap space, the Jaguars could use the franchise tag on starting left tackle Cam Robinson to keep him from entering the open market as a free agent. But the question is whether the Jaguars deem him vital enough to keep him around for another season with the tag or sign him to an extension?
Author: The Florida Times-Union on MSN.com
